{
  "stem": "10905.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was one large washroom with the running cold water and taps for women, one for men.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And also a latrine there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was also a smaller area where between the men's and women's barracks where you could wash, but, you know, didn't have latrines, and didn't have--",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- it was-- you could wash it outdoor, but it was as if a fence had been built with reeds, posted reeds.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Quite a bit further away were the latrines where you sat to move your bowels.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just like open, like slip trenches.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, like slip trenches.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was covered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And near there to the end were the watch towers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "To our right were Russians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And to the left were Dutch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, we were very, very privileged.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were the most privileged people ever, I think, in a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Nobody had to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Even when things broke down, we didn't have to be repair it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody in the camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody in our group had to work, except for my father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a physician.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had something that was so unusual.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a hospital barrack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our own-- our own section, our own section.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had one barrack that was a hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I saw my-- my second birth there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 1,300, I believe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] At least Hungarians, were together--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hungarian Jews.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, everybody was supposed to have been Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were together and life was rather boring.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, you were hungry because there was very little food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But every morning, every morning at 5 o'clock, rain or shine, it was appel you have to get up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all counting the people and counting the people and counting--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Outside.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody have to get on line.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
